projects.Name: Toy Corner
projects.Description: This toy corner project delivered a visually eye-catching eCommerce website. Featuring user-friendly color navigation, secure authentication is done with Firebase. The engaging home page has 10-12 sections, and all product and product management are handled using the MERN stack. React framer-motion is also used here, and a 404 page is added for error handling.
